---
const {
	id = 'Lorem Ipsum',

	copyEyebrow = 'Lorem Ipsum',
	copyHeadline = 'Lorem Ipsum',

	imageAlt = 'Lorem Ipsum',
	imageLoading = 'eager',
} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="mobell-uxb-wrapper" id="scroll-to-mobell">
	<div class="mobell-uxb-glow"></div>
	<img
		class="mobell-uxb-image"
		alt="Three phones displaying various screens from an app called Mobell."
		src="./assets/mobell/mobell-product-shot.png"
		loading="eager"
	/>
	<div class="mobell-uxb-copy">
		<h3>Mobell Service</h3>
		<h2>Improving accessibility, from hackathon idea to&nbsp;product</h2>
		<p>
			Mobell aims to make society more inclusive to people with disabilities and, as a result,
			make greater independence accessible to all. This service suite for businesses and their
			customers was conceived during the 2019 Camp PolyHacks Hackathon, winning 1st Place and
			“Best Use of Satellite Technology by&nbsp;Northrop&nbsp;Grumman”.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="boltabout-uxb-wrapper">
	<div class="boltabout-uxb-glow"></div>
	<img
		class="boltabout-uxb-image"
		alt="iPad displaying people on BoltAbout bikes, with the BoltAbout logo in the corner."
		src="./assets/boltabout/boltabout-product-shot.png"
		loading="lazy"
	/>
	<div class="boltabout-uxb-copy">
		<h3>BoltAbout Dashboard</h3>
		<h2>Streamlining the employee UX via Lean/6σ methodologies</h2>
		<p>
			Driven by a pursuit of constant improvement, my team and I were tasked with identifying
			inefficiencies to streamline BoltAbout&rsquo;s internal processes. This work utilized
			Lean/Six Sigma and UX Design methodologies to implement changes that not only
			drastically improve the employee experience, but also continue to save
			the&nbsp;company&nbsp;money.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="cp-uxb-wrapper">
	<div class="cp-uxb-glow"></div>
	<img
		class="cp-uxb-image"
		alt="Phone displaying a list of events from a Cal Poly events application."
		src="./assets/cp-events/cp-events-product-shot.png"
		loading="lazy"
	/>
	<div class="cp-uxb-copy">
		<h3>Cal Poly Events App</h3>
		<h2>Facilitating event discovery via research &amp;&nbsp;design</h2>
		<p>
			The end goal for this project was to re-envision Cal Poly&rsquo;s brand in an authentic
			and modern way by incorporating Material Design language in conjunction with user
			research and Cal Poly’s branding guidelines. This work and its associated insights were
			later used for inspiration by the Cal Poly app design team for development of their
			redesigned student&nbsp;application.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>

<style lang="scss">
	.mobell-uxb-wrapper button,
.boltabout-uxb-wrapper button,
.cp-uxb-wrapper button {
	cursor: not-allowed;
}

.mobell-uxb-wrapper {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
	grid-template-rows: auto;
	margin: 23vh auto;
	max-width: 100em;
	max-height: 100em;
	min-height: 40em;
	column-gap: 5%;
}

.mobell-uxb-glow {
	align-self: center;
	grid-column: 1/3;
	grid-row: 1;
	width: 30em;
	height: 30em;
	background: radial-gradient(
		ellipse closest-side,
		rgb(248, 161, 0) 0%,
		rgba(248, 181, 0, 0.1) 70%,
		rgba(248, 181, 0, 0) 100%
	);
	transform: scale(2) translateX(2em);
	opacity: 0.5;
	transition: ease 1s;
}

.mobell-uxb-image {
	grid-row: 1;
	grid-column: 1/3;
	transform: scale(1.3);
	transform-origin: right;
	transition: ease 1s;
}

.mobell-uxb-copy {
	grid-column: 3/5;
	grid-row: 1;
	margin-right: 4em;
	align-self: center;
	z-index: 1;
	max-width: 40em;
	transition: ease 1s;
}

.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-glow {
	transform: scale(2.7) translateX(2em);
}

.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-image {
	transform: scale(1.3) translateX(0.3em);
}

.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-copy {
	transform: translateX(-0.3em);
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 70em) {
	.mobell-uxb-wrapper {
		column-gap: 0;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-glow {
		transform: scale(1.7) translateX(-2em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-image {
		transform: scale(1.3) translateX(-2em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-copy {
		margin-right: 3em;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-glow {
		transform: scale(1.7) translateX(-2em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-image {
		transform: scale(1.3) translateX(-2em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-copy {
		transform: translateX(0);
	}
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 50em) {
	.mobell-uxb-wrapper {
		margin: 0 auto 10vh;
		grid-template-rows: 31em auto;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-glow {
		grid-column: 1/-1;
		transform: scale(1.5) translateX(-1em);
		width: auto;
		height: 25em;
		margin-bottom: -10em;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-image {
		transform: scale(1.5) translateX(-1em);
		transform-origin: top;
		grid-column: 1/-1;
		width: auto;
		height: 60vh;
		min-height: 25em;
		max-height: 28em;
		margin: 5em auto -5em;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-copy {
		padding: 3em 2em 0;
		grid-column: 1/-1;
		grid-row: 2;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: none;
		background: linear-gradient(
			0deg,
			var(--bg-layer-base) 0%,
			var(--bg-layer-base) 80%,
			rgba(33, 32, 36, 0.8) 90%,
			rgba(33, 32, 36, 0.5) 94%,
			rgba(33, 32, 36, 0.3) 96%,
			rgba(33, 32, 36, 0) 100%
		);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-copy p,
	.mobell-uxb-copy h2 {
		max-width: 550px;
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-glow {
		transform: scale(1.5) translateX(-1em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-image {
		transform: scale(1.5) translateX(-1em);
	}

	.mobell-uxb-wrapper:hover .mobell-uxb-copy {
		transform: translateX(0);
	}

	@media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
		.mobell-uxb-copy {
			background: linear-gradient(
				0deg,
				var(--bg-layer-base) 0%,
				var(--bg-layer-base) 80%,
				rgba(225, 225, 225, 0.8) 90%,
				rgba(225, 225, 225, 0.5) 94%,
				rgba(225, 225, 225, 0.3) 96%,
				rgba(225, 225, 225, 0) 100%
			);
		}
	}
}

